## Context Integration Notes

### "COME OUT" CHAIN — Extraction Before Judgment
v45 "My people, go ye out of the midst of her" → Jer 51:6 → Isa 52:11 → 2 Cor 6:17 → Rev 18:4 (verbatim quote)
Pattern: God extracts covenant people before destroying embedded system = RAPTURE_GATHERING principle

### RULER AGAINST RULER → WARS/RUMORS 
v46 "ruler against ruler" = OT source for Mat 24:6-7 "wars/rumors" + "nation against nation"
Jeremiah: context of Babylon's fall || Jesus: BIRTH_PAINS preceding Jerusalem destruction
Same vocabulary, different cycles

### STONE INTO EUPHRATES → MILLSTONE INTO SEA
vv63-64: stone + book → Euphrates → "Babylon sink, shall not rise"
Rev 18:21: millstone → sea → "Babylon thrown down, found no more"
Escalation: stone → millstone || river → sea
Jeremiah = prophetic-oracle origin of CAST_INTO_SEA pattern

### PERPETUAL SLEEP (NEW SYMBOL)
v57 "sleep a perpetual sleep and not wake" (+ v39)
WINE→SLEEP→SUDDEN_DESTRUCTION chain: judgment through intoxication/stupor
Dan 5 = narrative fulfillment (Belshazzar feast→death that night)
Links 1 Thess 5:3-7: sudden destruction on those who SLEEP

### HEAVEN/EARTH CELEBRATION
v48 "Heaven and earth...shall sing for Babylon" → Rev 18:20 "Rejoice over her, thou heaven"
Direct quotation. Cosmic scale indicates trans-historical fulfillment

### MOUNT UP TO HEAVEN (NEW SYMBOL)
v53 "mount up to heaven...fortify the height" echoes Gen 11:4 Babel tower
Human ambition to reach heaven by effort = founding→final boast bookend

