51:6,45 "come out" → 18:4 verbatim || 51:9 judgment→heaven → 18:5 sins→heaven
51:8 suddenly fallen → 18:2 via Isa 21:9 || 51:7 golden cup → 17:4+18:3
51:48 heaven sing → 18:20 || 51:63-64 stone sink → 18:21 millstone
51:57 perpetual sleep → 18:8 one day death || 51:58 fire → 18:8 burned
51:49 slain all earth → 18:24 blood all slain
