### FULFILLMENT AUDIT: 539 BC vs UNFULFILLED
539 BC fulfilled PATTERN: people out (Cyrus decree), rulers fell (Belshazzar), spoilers from north (Medes), sudden feast-fall (Dan 5)
NOT fulfilled SCALE: desolate forever, shall not rise, walls broken, burned with fire, cosmic celebration
Gap = what Rev 18 fills: global Babylon-system full fulfillment

