### JER 25:10 TRANSFER PATTERN
"Voice bridegroom/bride + millstones + candle" formula: first against JUDAH (Jer 7:34,16:9,25:10) → Rev 18:22-23 against Babylon
Covenant-judgment vocabulary transfers from unfaithful bride to corrupting harlot

